about.summary: Tools for multivariate nonparametrics, as location tests based on marginal ranks, spatial median and spatial signs computation, Hotelling's T-test, estimates of shape are implemented.

name: r-icsnp
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '1.1-1' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-icsnp
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/ICSNP_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/ICSNP/ICSNP_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: cd9d70977c448e46dd37b718e9127859cb7d081579f81897c652d6c66798c0fd

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 2
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}              # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}        # [win]
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}            # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_cxx') }}      # [win]
    - {{ posix }}filesystem        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}make
    - {{ posix }}sed               # [win]
    - {{ posix }}coreutils         # [win]
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-ics
    - r-mvtnorm
  run:
    - r-base
    - {{ native }}gcc-libs         # [win]
    - r-ics
    - r-mvtnorm

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('ICSNP')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('ICSNP')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=ICSNP
  license: GPL (>= 2)
  summary: Tools for multivariate nonparametrics, as location tests based on marginal ranks,
    spatial median and spatial signs computation, Hotelling's T-test, estimates of shape
    are implemented.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file: '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - MathiasHaudgaard
    - FrodePedersen
    - ArneKr
